          </h3>
          <a
            href="mailto:strefazmianpoznan@gmail.com"
            class="mt-1 block text-lg font-light text-foreground transition-colors hover:text-accent-warm"
          >
            strefazmianpoznan@gmail.com
          </a>
        </div>

        <div>
